sentences: Jang Jae-in (Hangul: 장재인, born June 6, 1991), also known as Jang Jane, is a South Korean singer-songwriter known for her unique voice.
Jang became well known after she finished third in the South Korean reality television series Superstar K 2 in 2010.
Jang was born in Gangjin-gun, Jeollanam-do, South Korea, on June 6, 1991.
In 2020 her first studio albumThe Quest of Anxiety was released.
In 2010, Jang appeared on Superstar K2, placing third.
